Source.Name: python-numba
Source.Summary: NumPy aware dynamic Python compiler using LLVM
Source.Description: Numba is an open source, NumPy-aware optimizing compiler for Python sponsored by Anaconda, Inc. It uses the LLVM compiler project to generate machine code from Python syntax.
